    <item>
      <title>Regain Decayed Master Sword</title>
      <author>Ancient Link</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/624667</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/624667#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">e82a9a342d9a63a9a1e36904e73329575e358285</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 Oct 2025 07:19:01 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68e0c2367fb07.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68e0c21c70f0d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68e0c4df2226f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68e0c4c8bc276.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68e0c4e3d3650.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68e0c55bd0bae.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68e0c4c98ac15.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68e0c4c97ca98.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68e0c4c4af5ab.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68e0c4c8886fa.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68e0c4de6dcbe.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68e0c4e32ebf5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;I've always been sad about the fact that you lose the Decayed Master Sword after completing the Great Sky Island, and have always been trying to find a way to get it back, so I made this is a simple mod that allows you to regain the Decayed Master Sword.&lt;br&gt;      What it does:&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;-Places the Decayed Master Sword in front of the Mother Goddess Statue in the Forgotten Temple.&lt;/span&gt; (I was doing something completely different with that map file, but ended up just putting the Decayed Master Sword there instead. I'll probably move it to somewhere in the Room of Awakening on the Great Sky Island when I figure out how.)&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;-Makes it fuseable, with the Master Sword's ghost fuse.&lt;br&gt;-Gives it the Guard Enhance/Parry ability.&lt;br&gt;-Makes it unbreakable.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;      Unfortunately, I was unable to figure out how to stop the game from removing the Decayed Master Sword from your inventory after every reloaded save, but it does respawn in the Forgotten Temple whenever you transport there, so that makes up for that, I guess. &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;I highly recommend using Zuggle-Overload to display it in your house&lt;/span&gt;, which is really easy in patch 1.1.0, which is the only patch I can get my Ryujinx to run at the moment, so I haven't tested this mod on any other version. I assume that if you install it with TKMM, it'll be compatible with most, if not all versions, but again, I cannot test that. &lt;br&gt;      I'd love to hear it TKMM does make it work with other versions, so if anyone tries it, feel free to comment.</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/display_decayed_master_sword.zip" type="application/zip"/>
      <category>Overworld</category>
      <category>Map</category>
    </item>
