ebanana.com/img/ss/mods/654f2a8447947.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/655881a62d941.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/654f2a1c021f1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/654f2a36b2879.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/654f2a48c9cd3.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/654f2a5a71caa.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/654f2aaa0e932.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/654f2b0adf191.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65543d6081cd0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6565b8acb7086.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6565b8acf2954.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6565b8acea458.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6565b8ad122b7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6565b8ad1842d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6565b8ad16374.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6565b8ad1aab4.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6565b8ad247be.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6551ec4028f58.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/654f2b5696c73.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/661bdca1cf422.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/661bdab137273.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/661bdbccd476a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/661bdbf17cce1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/661bdc034af78.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/661bdc5bc563d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; v3.2 release&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;We've finally passed the halfway mark of the planned development, the wolf link mod is heading into its final chapter.&lt;br&gt;The development hit some bumps, so this time is just a minor update. We'll try to wrap up this mod in the next update.&lt;br&gt;Special thanks to ezfastpaws and v--r for their great contributions to the armor adaptation work, and heck for his dedicated bug hunting.&lt;br&gt;Also thanks to all you guys enjoying our pupper. Have fun!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;[ New Features ]&lt;br&gt;You can switch the head size between standard and smaller&lt;br&gt;You can change the body fur color between brown and green&lt;br&gt;You can switch the Evil spirit mask's appearance&lt;br&gt;You can use permanently awakened master sword&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;[ Additional Adopted Armor Set ]&lt;br&gt;Radiant Set&lt;br&gt;Rubber Set&lt;br&gt;Depths Set&lt;br&gt;Dark Set&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Mask of Awakening(Merged &lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/538212"&gt;Mask of Furry Awakening Mod for The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom | TOTK Mods&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br&gt;Majora's Mask&lt;br&gt;Ravio's Hood&lt;br&gt;Cece Hat&lt;br&gt;Sand Boots&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Diamond Circlet&lt;br&gt;Ruby Circlet&lt;br&gt;Sapphire Circlet&lt;br&gt;Topaz Earrings&lt;br&gt;Opal Earrings&lt;br&gt;Amber Earrings&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;[ Improvement ]&lt;br&gt;Compatible with ver1.4.0 and ver1.4.2 of totk(if it doesn't work well, pls let us know)&lt;br&gt;Fixed some reported bugs&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;You can play as Wolf Link.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Now we have essentially achieved most of the features envisioned for the initial stages of the project, except for the rest armor and new voice.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;We could never make this mod come true without the fantastic wolf link design from &lt;a href="https://twitter.com/elranno" target="_blank"&gt;Marc Knelsen&lt;/a&gt;, and the best support &amp; help from &lt;a href="https://twitter.com/MelonSpeedruns" target="_blank"&gt;MelonSpeedruns&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a class="MemberLink" href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2750039" data-id="member_2750039"&gt;draconteur&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;And I'm thrilled to see more and more like-minded individuals spontaneously getting involved in the development of the mod and its derivatives, like HenryLittle, who solved the mystery issue about compatible with mac os, and &lt;a class="MemberLink" href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2563536" data-id="member_2563536"&gt;EzFastPaws&lt;/a&gt;, the hero who making armor adaption is no longer a challenge.&lt;br&gt;your participation has given the pupper endless possibilities. Thank you all guys!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Also, A big thanks to KillzXGaming and everyone else for making the modding of totk possible.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="SelectedElement"&gt;And you. Modding is a tedious, brain-draining, and lonely work, without the continued support from you guys, this mod wouldn't even have a ver 2.0. Thank you so much! Have fun with your pupper :)&lt;/div&gt;</description>
