      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68ade1a133725.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68ade1b242be8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68ade1c7bcd34.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68ade1d9b97ed.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Ember set 1.1.2&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This update improves the quality of movement in the face, adds variety for those who do not want the long stiletto style nails, and it fixes the invisible face paint issue!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: New nail style options, base nails are no longer painted.&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Face paint is no longer invisible.&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Improvement&lt;/em&gt;: Weight painting on the face is improved with less jagged edges during movement, and no longer has floating vertices parented to the wrong vertex groups around the neck.&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod is a model replacement for the Ember Set that is fit for Linkle! It has adjusted proportions to fit Linkle.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; Additionally the armor now has stiletto nails on both hands and heeled boots so that you can absorb the sun with extra style!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Note that this mod was developed for the use with the official Linkle mod however it was developed without association to the Linkle mod's creators -</description>
