      <guid isPermaLink="false">0cee912eaf7b70eb50394a7e376cff9d7b9d578c</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Sep 2025 19:46:32 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68b89236e966b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68b8931761301.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is a music pack inspired by this awesome mod, &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/49593"&gt;Actic's Faithful Zelda Music Replacement&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I would have never been able to do this without the huge help of &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1719480"&gt;Cattail&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I did not replace all the soundtracks, since I wanted the game to still kept its unique touch.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Here is the track list:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Field battle ( ground and Cave ) Easy &amp; Medium,&lt;br&gt;      Dungeon battle&lt;br&gt;      &lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ni6mW_uCVb8" target="_blank"&gt;The legend of zelda: Ocarina of Time 3D - Battle theme&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;      &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/WSvcLjIOKh8?feature=shared" target="_blank"&gt;The legend of zelda: &lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zToujlzS5PI" target="_blank"&gt;Ocarina of Time - Battle Theme (Epic orchestral cover)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Field battle ( ground and cave ) Hard,&lt;br&gt;      Shrine battle&lt;br&gt;      &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/WSvcLjIOKh8?feature=shared" target="_blank"&gt;The legend of zelda: &lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wu8V1Ob6hfQ" target="_blank"&gt;Ocarina of Time - Middle Boss Battle Arrangement&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ganondorf dungeon battle&lt;br&gt;     &lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q1CxVXH9uhQ" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://youtu.be/WSvcLjIOKh8?feature=shared" target="_blank"&gt;The legend of zelda: Twilight Princess - Stallord&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Field Bosses ( Bokoblin boss, Hinox, Talus, Frox, Flux construct  )&lt;br&gt;      &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/WSvcLjIOKh8?feature=shared" target="_blank"&gt;The legend of zelda: &lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9RgMViW6T9I" target="_blank"&gt;Twilight Princess - Fyrus Orchestral Arrangement&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Gleeok&lt;br&gt;      &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/WSvcLjIOKh8?feature=shared" target="_blank"&gt;The legend of zelda: &lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GsfxzV204Kw" target="_blank"&gt;Ocarina of Time - Dinosaur Battle Arrangement&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Molduga&lt;br&gt;      &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/zBabAhL8yS0?feature=shared" target="_blank"&gt;Hyrule warriors: Age of calamity - Intense battle against the molduga&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Phantom Ganon&lt;br&gt;      &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/t5vVUwLQV78?feature=shared" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://youtu.be/WSvcLjIOKh8?feature=shared" target="_blank"&gt;The legend of zelda: Ocarina of Time - Ganondorf Battle Orchestral arrangement&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Goron middle boss,&lt;br&gt;      Gerudo village defense&lt;br&gt;     &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/WSvcLjIOKh8?feature=shared" target="_blank"&gt;The legend of zelda: a link between worlds - Battle theme 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Lithogohma&lt;br&gt;     &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/EGbOMdFXmRM?feature=shared" target="_blank"&gt;The legend of zelda: a link to the past - Anger of the guardians orchestral arrangement&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Mucktorok&lt;br&gt;     &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/9YNta7lqqJ4?feature=shared" target="_blank"&gt;The legend of zelda: Tears of the kingdom - Mucktorok theme dark souls style&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Queen gibdo&lt;br&gt;     &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/r8vE-cYqT3I?feature=shared" target="_blank"&gt;The legend of zelda: Tears of the kingdom - Queen Gibdo ( epic )&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Seized construct&lt;br&gt;     &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/p9Ht6EMtN8A?feature=shared" target="_blank"&gt;Hyrule warriors: Age of calamity - Fight the battle - Tested guardian&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ruins&lt;br&gt;     &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/kAkJdviV-c8?feature=shared" target="_blank"&gt;The legend of zelda: Ocarina of Time - Title theme ( piano cover )&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Temple of time ( sky )&lt;br&gt;     &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/pmyjfsq_25A?feature=shared" target="_blank"&gt;The legend of zelda: Ocarina of time - Temple of time ( orchestrated, fan made )&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Goron village ( unsolved )&lt;br&gt;      &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/JOAm8agoStk?feature=shared" target="_blank"&gt;The legend of zelda: Ocarina of time - Goron village&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Goron village ( solved )&lt;br&gt;     &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/Yes367rnRj0?feature=shared" target="_blank"&gt;The legend of zelda: Twilight princess - Death mountain&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Gerudo village ( unsolved )&lt;br&gt;     &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/pmGdJ0XCzHI?feature=shared" target="_blank"&gt;The legend of zelda: Ocarina of time - Gerudo village ( slowed and relaxing acoustic cover )&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Gerudo village ( solved )&lt;br&gt;     &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/0hEYvdMoF2g?feature=shared" target="_blank"&gt;The legend of zelda: Ocarina of time - Gerudo valley&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Hateno village&lt;br&gt;     &lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4Yh6KPjCynU" target="_blank" class="SelectedElement"&gt;The legend of zelda: A link to the past - Kakariko village orchestral arrangement&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Lost woods&lt;br&gt;     &lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N9Clmr94zGY" target="_blank"&gt;The Legend of zelda: Twilight princess - Sacred grove&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Horse ride&lt;br&gt;     &lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=whHZxFLT7a0" target="_blank"&gt;The legend of zelda: A link to the past - Hyrule field&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;I had to do a bit of editing on some tracks, particularly on the large bosses, since there are 2 phases.</description>
